{{else}}
1. Create test class extending BaseTest
2. Add @ExtendWith(TestWatcher.class) annotation
3. Add @Test methods with appropriate @Tag annotations
4. Run: `mvn clean test -Dgroups=your-tag`
{{/if}}

### Adding New Page Objects

1. Create class extending BasePage
2. Define locators as private variables
3. Implement page-specific methods
4. Use in test classes

### Adding New Utilities

1. Create utility class in `utils` package
2. Add static helper methods
3. Use Log class for logging
4. Import and use in tests

